1
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:48,120
Your case is already closed, right?

2
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,840
Closed as an accident.

3
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,520
You orchestrated these accidents.

4
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,280
Because you knew that

5
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,960
if you called the police,

6
00:01:58,320 --> 00:02:00,320
Mu Weijie would lash out.

7
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,600
But if you killed him yourself,

8
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:05,000
you would be punished by the law.

9
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:05,960
So,

10
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,440
you orchestrated all these accidents.

11
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,720
I pulled off an accident.

12
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,680
I'm so amazing.

13
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,140
Where is the evidence?

14
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,800
I don't think I'm that capable.

15
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,120
Of course you are.

16
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:41,450
The final determined cause of death for Mu Weijie

17
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:44,960
was an overdose of aphrodisiacs,

18
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,360
which led to sudden cardiac death.

19
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,760
So what you had to do,

20
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,120
as the first step,

21
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:56,600
all you had to do was wait,

22
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,700
wait for him to let his guard down.

23
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:01,560
Wait until he trusts you completely.

24
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,000
Can you take a look for me?

25
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,280
We're out of tape.

26
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,960
Does anyone have extra?

27
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,880
There's some in the teacher's office.

28
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,960
I'll get it for you.

29
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:17,800
Thanks.

30
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,600
It's like this.

31
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:23,360
Mu Weijie's office has no surveillance

32
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,200
or door lock.

33
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,690
Plus, you saw him taking his medicine.

34
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,720
So,

35
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,740
as long as the timing is right,

36
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:33,300
you could easily get that bottle of medicine

37
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:36,920
and take a few pills out.

38
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,240
Step two.

39
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,760
You took these pills

40
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,880
to the university chemistry lab.

41
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:51,480
You took applied chemistry as an elective in college,

42
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,640
so you took full advantage of that.

43
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,120
You took the powder from these pills,

44
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,920
recrystallized and refined it,

45
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:00,800
and put it back into a capsule.

46
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,720
At this concentration,

47
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:06,080
it's dangerous for a normal man to take,

48
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:09,120
let alone someone with heart problems.

49
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,080
My colleagues checked.

50
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:15,920
The female student in the studio who took the applied chemistry course.

51
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,240
You were the only one.

52
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,600
So I conclude

53
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,720
that you

54
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,560
are the killer.

55
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,800
Unfortunately,

56
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,960
the chemistry lab is used every day,

57
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,330
so all traces are long gone.

58
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,480
Sound logic.

59
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,920
Good theory.

60
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,920
But how can you be so sure

61
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:45,320
I could make him take that high-concentration pill that day?

62
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,520
That's your most brilliant move.

63
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,930
You didn't need to guarantee when he would take the pill.

64
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:58,159
Because Mu Weijie would continue to demand sex from you.

65
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,480
You knew

66
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,520
this pill,

67
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,080
he would take it sooner or later.

68
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,520
To accelerate this outcome,

69
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,800
you stopped at nothing.

70
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:12,840
No matter how much you despised and hated him,

71
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:15,780
you still chose to actively cater to him,

72
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,740
so he would take that pill sooner.

73
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,160
Over here.

74
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,120
My Danaë

75
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,120
has finally figured it out.

76
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,880
But your carefully designed script

77
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,720
ultimately

78
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,760
harmed your friend.

79
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:04,280
Mu Weijie was originally going to find you that day.

80
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:07,920
But he saw Lin Rongrong returning instead.

81
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,680
Unknowingly,

82
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:33,280
that pill had already taken effect.

83
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,440
His blood began to rush.

84
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,760
[Breathing heavily]

85
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,240
Due to the high concentration,

86
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,100
his consciousness began to blur,

87
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:44,120
and he gradually lost his reason.

88
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,640
Mr. Mu, you can't do this.

89
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,840
Mr. Mu!

90
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,760
Mr. Mu!

91
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,480
What a perfect story.

92
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,800
It's as if you saw it with your own eyes.

93
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,120
What a pity.

94
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,720
You still have no evidence.

95
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,240
I will listen to the police

96
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,040
and stay here for a full 24 hours.

97
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,640
However,

98
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:21,000
within these 24 hours,

99
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,880
if you can't find any evidence,

100
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,560
we might never see each other again.

101
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:33,920
Hey.

102
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,680
Ms. Zhuang had us stake out here all day.

103
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,800
Lin Rongrong hasn't made a peep.

104
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,620
What do you think she's doing in her room?

105
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,650
The curtains are drawn.

106
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,760
Is she going to sleep at this hour?

107
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,520
I don't think so.

108
00:07:57,480 --> 00:08:00,600
If you hadn't thrown yourself at my husband and seduced him,

109
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:03,120
why would he have chosen you?

110
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,640
Recently, news of a young art teacher

111
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:10,300
passing away unexpectedly has attracted widespread attention.

112
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:29,160
It's not like that. It's not like that.

113
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:32,120
I'm obviously the victim here.

114
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,770
What's going on?

115
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,240
Oh no.

116
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,200
Lin Rongrong.

117
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,560
Lin Rongrong.

118
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,440
Lin Rongrong.

119
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,120
To the hospital. To the hospital.

120
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:48,880
Drive.

121
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,480
Brother, I'll go get the car.

122
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,000
Lin Rongrong.

123
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,160
Lin Rongrong.

124
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,000
Hello?

125
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,520
Lao Fang, say that again.

126
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,600
Captain Zhuang, I'm at Mancheng Hospital now.

127
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,400
Come quickly.

128
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,340
Lin Rongrong committed suicide.

129
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,960
You and Xiaobai wait at the hospital.

130
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,280
Lin Rongrong can't die.

131
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,600
I'll be right there.

132
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,600
Take me to see her.

133
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:37,240
Just let me see her,

134
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,660
and I'll give you a satisfactory answer.

135
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
How is it? What's the situation now?

136
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,400
How is Rongrong?

137
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,720
Fortunately, she was brought in just in time.

138
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,640
After emergency treatment,

139
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,880
she is out of danger.

140
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,040
But the patient's condition is not very good.

141
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,320
If possible,

142
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,050
please keep as quiet as you can.

143
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,260
Ask whatever you want to ask quickly.

144
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,720
Let me in.

145
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,200
Let me in.

146
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:12,080
Officer Zhuang,

147
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,520
I beg you.

148
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,880
Please let me in

149
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,800
to see Rongrong.

150
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,960
Please.

151
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,200
Xiaoyue.

152
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,240
Xiaoyue.

153
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,280
Why did you try to commit suicide?

154
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:44,440
Answer me. Why did you try to commit suicide?

155
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:53,280
What would I do if you died?

156
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,320
Xiaoyue.

157
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,880
I'm sorry.

158
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,960
I was so stupid.

159
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:06,400
But I really didn't know what to do.

160
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,800
Does it hurt?

161
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,800
I'm sorry.

162
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:31,480
This is all because of me.

163
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:35,440
I failed to protect you.

164
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,840
How could that be, Xiaoyue?

165
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:46,240
You got involved in this mess because of me.

166
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,280
I'm really sorry.

167
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:51,640
I really didn't expect Mu Weijie to do that to you.

168
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,640
It's all my fault.

169
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,440
Stop talking nonsense.

170
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,840
We are the victims.

171
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,680
Qiaoyue,

172
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:04,920
I will never blame you.

173
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,720
You are my best friend.

174
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,760
Since we were kids,

175
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,960
every time I was wronged,

176
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:17,600
you were always the first to be by my side.

177
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:25,080
We promised to be together forever.

178
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:28,280
I'll go wherever you go.

179
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,160
I'm sorry.

180
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:35,120
I chickened out this time.

181
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,240
Rongrong.

182
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,840
Recover well.

183
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,000
Live well.

184
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,200
It's all in the past now.

185
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,760
I will protect you.

186
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,220
Wait for me.

187
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,760
Officer Zhuang.

188
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,600
I plead guilty.
